			"invoker_wex"		"Active Wex orbs increase Invoker's attack speed, and more importantly movement speed which can be useful for chasing down enemies."
			"invoker_invoke"		"Invoke will not cost mana or go on cooldown if the only effect is to swap the positions of existing spells.

Whenever a new spell is invoked, the oldest of his two currently Invoked spells is removed from selection.
"
			"invoker_cold_snap"		"The freeze stun only triggers on damage greater than 10 after reductions.

Cold Snap is very strong when combined with any spell that deals damage over time, as each small damage instance procs the mini-stun and damage. (Meteor / Forge Spirits)
"
			"invoker_ghost_walk"		"Ghost Walk can be used as an escape or as a ganking and scouting tool."
			"invoker_tornado"		"Units are invulnerable while affected by Tornado, and the damage is dealt when landing.
The damage is applied upon losing the Tornado debuff. 

Can deal up to 115/160/205/250/295/340/385(430 with Aghanim's)

Multiple Combo usages:

1.Tornado into sunstrike
2. Tornado into sunstrike into Meteor
3. Tornado into Ice Wall into Cold Snap(you can follow up with Alacrity on yourself).

Use it as an initiating tool.
"
			"invoker_emp"		"Will not affect cycloned units (Tornado or Eul's Scepter of Divinity).
