"
			"invoker_chaos_meteor"		"Deals main damage to enemy units under meteor every 0.5 seconds and burns enemies for smaller damage over 3 seconds.

Combine it with:
1.Tornado
2. Eul's Scepter
"
			"invoker_sun_strike"		"Can be used globally.
Invoker gains experience with kills from Sun Strike, even if they happen outside of experience range.

Constantly check the map for low HP enemy heroes and try to snipe them.

Setups:
1. Eul's Scepter
2. Tornado
3. Any lockdown from allied heroes
"
			"invoker_forge_spirit"		"Casting this ability will replace currently summoned Forged Spirits.

Get the level 15 talent since that will further increase your potential of split-pushing/focusing certain heroes.
"
